{"tid":1256002,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[陰 謀 論] 最 終 目 標 係 解 放 中 環","createTime":"2019-06-24T18:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T15:12:55.000Z","uid":27415,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"89189993eade53f5a67105d899876c8d4f39a026","tid":1256002,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:39:43.000Z","msg":"會唔會係政府學識左玩「偷襲」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府特登先硬推罪犯條例，引大家群起去反對，<br />\n等大家目光去曬罪犯條例而忽視佢其他動作。<br />\n<br />\n宜家係罪犯條例所引發既爭議到一路拖拉住，<br />\n一黎可以耗費肯出黎個班民眾既政治熱情，同時係到慢慢扮被動，再加上CCTVB呢D喉舌去帶風向，等中間派既民眾由「無意見」變成「撐政府去執法」既心態。<br />\n<br />\n借鑑上次雨革，每次呢D大型運動之後，都會迎黎一段「政治冷感期」。<br />\n<br />\n就好似你做完愛，射左幾次之後，就進入聖人mode一樣。<br />\n<br />\n就係呢個時候，政府就唔聲唔聲咁推「解放中環」，最後，分分鐘話咁易就pass到，得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d68a04cf7e2071c3b0253e94c1f606ad9b330f0","tid":1256002,"uid":27415,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:41:48.000Z","msg":"係咪要G爆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鄰國好似好等錢洗喎<br />\n<br />\n唔係搶中環呢D黃金地，就係想利用罪犯條例去引曬D驚死有錢佬返去抄家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e36b7388df4da30a8f518daeaaf046d6b03923","tid":1256002,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:43:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f46d11172e165ca62f58e66e357f3b59c11a62","tid":1256002,"uid":27415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T18:49:12.000Z","msg":"如果佢地識捉心理，佢地就真係好醒目。<br />\n<br />\n當大家開始覺得罪犯條例修訂都爭取唔到D咩，個無力感慢慢增加既時候，先走去推D咁重磅既嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb25b9154eb62161f5de3a38962b4dd87c61c52","tid":1256002,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}